<plot>Gian Luigi is a young aggressive financial consultant in Roma. He manages a huge amount of money, often without knowing who the owners are. He deposits his profits in Switzerland (evading the taxation). He is in touch with the richest persons in town; he has no problems with women. His life is an exaggeration after another. Once he meets a beautiful journalist that is investigating over a bribery affair. She is killed and from that moment on for Gian Luigi the situation starts to be more problematic.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?257929</url></doc>
